OL,6,FA care home in Northumberland has been
OL,7,Fplaced into special measures by the
OL,8,FCare Quality Comission (CQC) following
OL,9,Fconcerns of safety and staffing.
OL,11,FNorthlands Care home in Morpeth, which
OL,12,Flooks after people with physical
OL,13,Fdisabilities, older people, and people
OL,14,Fwith dementia, was rated inadequate
OL,15,Ffollowing an inspection in December
OL,16,F2023.
