OL,6,FThe CQC said the assessment was
OL,7,Fprompted due to concerns they received
OL,8,Fin relation to keeping people safe,
OL,9,Fdelivering the right care, and
OL,10,Fstaffing.
OL,12,FParkside Care Limited, who run the
OL,13,Ffacility, said there has been "good
OL,14,Fand effective progress over the last
OL,15,Fthree months" and that they "hope to
OL,16,Freturn to a good rating as soon as
OL,17,Fpossible".
OL,19,FThe home supports up to 39 people at a
OL,20,Ftime and was looking after 37 people
OL,21,Fat the time of the inspection.
