OL,6,FThe CQC found that there had been a
OL,7,Fnumber of falls at the home or
OL,8,Funexplained bruising which weren't
OL,9,Falways identified or referred to the
OL,10,Fsafeguarding team.
OL,12,FStaff were also found to not always be
OL,13,Fsupporting people to drink enough
OL,14,Ffluids, including those at risk of
OL,15,Fchoking or using a feeding tube.
OL,17,FFollowing this inspection, the
OL,18,Fservice's overall rating dropped from
OL,19,Fgood to inadequate, as has the rating
OL,20,Ffor being safe and effective.
