OL,6,FThe "well-led" rating has dropped from
OL,7,Frequires improvement to inadequate. As
OL,8,Fthis was a focused inspection, caring
OL,9,Fand responsive were not included and
OL,10,Fremain rated good from their previous
OL,11,Finspection.
OL,13,FThe service is now in special
OL,14,Fmeasures, which means it will be kept
OL,15,Funder close review by CQC to keep
OL,16,Fpeople safe and it will be monitored
OL,17,Fto check sufficient improvements have
OL,18,Fbeen made.
