OL,6,FLinda Hirst, CQC deputy director of
OL,7,Foperations in the north, said: "When
OL,8,Fwe inspected Northlands Care Home, we
OL,9,Fwere disappointed to see a shortfall
OL,10,Fin strong leadership.
OL,12,F"We saw ineffective management
OL,13,Fstructures meant the provider couldn't
OL,14,Fmonitor the quality of care provided
OL,15,For know where improvements were needed
OL,16,Fto support people safely.
OL,18,F"During our visit, we found people
OL,19,Fweren't always safe from the risk of
OL,20,Favoidable harm.
