OL,6,F"At the time of the inspection the
OL,7,Fservice was in organisational
OL,8,Fsafeguarding with the local authority
OL,9,Fas there were multiple concerns about
OL,10,Fpeople's care and safety at the home.
OL,12,F"We found there had been a number of
OL,13,Ffalls at the home or unexplained
OL,14,Fbruising which weren't always
OL,15,Fidentified or referred to the
OL,16,Fsafeguarding team in a timely manner
OL,17,For being learned from to prevent
OL,18,Ffuture incidents.
