OL,6,F"We found staff weren't always
OL,7,Fsupporting people to drink enough
OL,8,Ffluids. Charts consistently showed
OL,9,Fpeople weren't drinking enough and
OL,10,Fcare plans didn't always show where
OL,11,Fpeople, including those at risk of
OL,12,Fchoking or using a feeding tube,
OL,13,Fneeded additional support to keep them
OL,14,Fsafe.
