OL,6,F"Additionally, we saw the provider
OL,7,Fdidn't always make sure staff had the
OL,8,Fskills, knowledge and experience to
OL,9,Fdeliver effective care and support.
OL,10,FThe local authority safeguarding team
OL,11,Fhad also highlighted areas where staff
OL,12,Fneeded more training, and the provider
OL,13,Fwas working with them to address
OL,14,Fissues.
