OL,6,F"We have told Northlands Care Home
OL,7,Fwhere we expect to see rapid and
OL,8,Fwidespread improvements and will
OL,9,Fcontinue to monitor them closely to
OL,10,Fkeep people safe while this happens.
OL,11,FWe will return to check on their
OL,12,Fprogress and won't hesitate to take
OL,13,Faction if people are not receiving the
OL,14,Fcare they have a right to expect."
