OL,6,FIn response to the findings of the
OL,7,Finspection, a spokesperson from
OL,8,FParkside Care Limited said: "We regret
OL,9,Fthat Northlands Care Home has fallen
OL,10,Fbelow the standards that we and the
OL,11,FCare Quality Commission expect. As
OL,12,Fnoted in the report, we were in the
OL,13,Fprocess of making improvements at the
OL,14,Ftime of the inspection in December and
OL,15,Fhave recruited an experienced new Head
OL,16,Fof Quality and Compliance. They are
OL,17,Fworking with colleagues on a
OL,18,Fcomprehensive plan to ensure that
OL,19,Fimprovements required to our record
OL,20,Fkeeping and procedures are made and
OL,21,Fsustained.
