OL,6,F"We have made good and effective
OL,7,Fprogress over the last three months
OL,8,Fsince the inspection and hope to
OL,9,Freturn to a Good rating as soon as
OL,10,Fpossible, in common with the other
OL,11,Fcare homes within our long-established
OL,12,Fgroup.
OL,14,F"We have already taken numerous steps
OL,15,Fto rectify the issues highlighted,
OL,16,Fincluding a review of resident care
OL,17,Fplanning, risk assessments, audits,
OL,18,Fand quality assurance.
